─γ─ Photon Heterogeneous Compute Engine

┌ γ ─────────────────────┐
│            ψ           │
│             ╲          │
│  ξ ──► λ ──► Δ ──► μ   │
│             ╱          │
│            π           │
└────────────────────────┘

─< Δ engine  >─────────────────────────
memory, threads, sync

─< π   gpu   >─────────────────────────
render & compute

─< μ   gui   >─────────────────────────
control interface

─< ξ network >─────────────────────────
ingest streams

─< λ  parse  >─────────────────────────
decode & store

─< ψ  synth  >─────────────────────────
analysis & synthesis


─< Build >─────────────────────────────
< https://github.com/lhr-solar/Photon/wiki/GettingStarted >

┌ linux ─────────────────┐
│ $ ./build              │
└────────────────────────┘

┌ windows ───────────────┐
│ > .\winBuild.ps1       │
└────────────────────────┘

to build on linux:
cmake -S . -B .artifacts -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release
cmake --build .artifacts -j20

if compiled for debug (no "release" flag)

enable tracy:

    make tracy

disable tracy:

    make notracy

to build on windows:
cmake -S . -B .artifacts -G Ninja -D CMAKE_C_COMPILER=clang -D CMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=clang++

build for release:
cmake -S . -B .artifacts -G Ninja -D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -D CMAKE_C_COMPILER=clang -D CMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=clang++
cmake --build .artifacts -j20

check for dependencies:
llvm-readobj.exe --needed-libs .artifacts\bin\Photon.exe

format:
cmake --build .artifacts --target format
